Spring 2024 Election Results

Author

Slater Dixon

Voting

Per the ASA Constitution and Election Code, 2024 Spring Elections were conducted using Ranked Choice Vote, also known as Single Transferable Vote. Results were tabulated using the R package vote. (2023)

President/Vice President

Annie Johnston was elected President and Prince Adhikari was elected Vice President by default.

Secretary

Carson Steichen was elected Secretary by default.
